                    <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
                    <span class="last-updated">Last updated: March 9, 2026</span>

                    <p>This Cookie Policy explains what cookies are, how Kidamame uses them on our website, and your
                        choices regarding their use.</p>

                    <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
                    <p>Cookies are small text files that are placed on your computer or mobile device when you visit a
                        website. They are widely used to make websites work, or work more efficiently, as well as to
                        provide information to the owners of the site.</p>

                    <h2>2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
                    <p>Currently, Kidamame is committed to providing a clean, privacy-first experience. Our website
                        (kidamame.com) uses minimal cookies. We do not use intrusive advertising or profiling cookies.
                    </p>

                    <p>When you visit our website, you may encounter a cookie consent banner (provided by Cookiebot). We
                        use this to respect your tracking preferences. By default, no non-essential cookies are loaded
                        unless requested by third-party embedded content or unless you explicitly give your consent.</p>

                    <h2>3. Types of Cookies We May Use</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Strictly Necessary Cookies:</strong> These are cookies that are required for the
                            operation of our website. They include, for example, cookies that enable basic functions
                            like page navigation.</li>
                        <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> We may use basic, anonymized analytics to understand how
                            visitors interact with our website to improve our web content. These do not track personal
                            data.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>4. Our Educational Apps</h2>
                    <p>Our educational apps designed for children (such as <strong>Kidamame Discovery</strong>) are
                        entirely offline and ad-free once downloaded. <strong>The apps do not use cookies or any
                            tracking technologies.</strong></p>

                    <h2>5. Managing Your Preferences</h2>
                    <p>You can manage your cookie preferences at any time through the cookie consent banner on our
                        website or by adjusting the settings in your web browser. Most browsers allow you to control
                        cookies through their settings preferences.</p>

